data.title: Lindsey Bradforf Pioneers of Homeopathy PDF
data.meta_description: Lindsey-Bradforf-Pioneers-of-homeopathy.pdf - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. The document discusses the provers who assisted Samuel Hahnemann in developing homeopathic medicines. It lists over 50 provers by name and the medicines they proved. Some of the key provers included E. Stapf, G.W. Gross, F. Hahnemann, C.F. Trinks, F. Hartman, and A. Haynel. Hahnemann carefully examined the proving reports from these early homeopathic pioneers.
